---
title: Double Braised Chicken Drumsticks with Potato Mash & Parsley
description: Braising is a great way to unleash all the flavour from these chicken drumsticks and the best part is how easy it is to do! Add
everything, like the chicken, veggies and mild spices into one pot and let it all come together. Serve up with a cheesy mash and
you’re good to go!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64d5aa1909d29015a857deb4-8098cbcb.jpeg
